window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Neko Goodbrush just wanted to spend a lazy day with his best friend: find some breakfast, explore the forest, maybe even take a nap beneath a tree. But when his fairy friend Talia is sprite-napped by a pixie-dust-addicted troll, Neko finds himself thrust into a whirlwind adventure that will test the limits of his courage and send him deep into the remote and dangerous depths of the Sylvanwood Forest that they call home.&nbsp;</p> <p>What is a three-foot-tall wolfkin supposed to do when nothing is what it seems, legends become real, and exiled forest deities run amok?&nbsp;</p> <p>Find out in this eagerly anticipated second volume of the Chronicles of Chalisaria!</p>"; 
